==English==
===Etymology===
From {{Arab.}} المركب الفرس (''al-markab al-faras''), "the saddle of the horse"
===Noun===
{{wikipedia|Markab}}
'''Markab'''

#{{star}}: A [[bluish]] [[star]] in the [[constellation]] of [[Pegasus]]; Alpha (α) Pegasi. It forms one of the corners of the square of Pegasus.
#{{star}}: A star in the constellation [[Puppis]]; Kappa (κ) Puppis.
#{{star}}: A star in the constellation [[Vela]]; Kappa (κ) Velorum.

===Synonym===
*[[Mankib]] (''Alpha Pegasi'')